TopicTitle: Stock02_Kerbal2 - Bill Kerman + EVA = ship destroyed + bill launches into end of universe.

Articles.Content:
Guys...lova ya and love this franchise.....but ya need to allow attachments.....this is kinda dumb in 2023.......

 

brand new campaign started at first game load from patch 02

  • KSP Version
    • - 10943457  appID  954850    updated 4/12/23 at 512am
  • Operating System and version  (Windows 10, Windows 11) - ---------------------------
  • CPU and GPU models, any other system information which could be relevant----------------
    • CPU - 12th Gen Intel(R) Core(TM) i9-12900K   3.19 GHz
    • ram -  32.0 GB (31.8 GB usable)
    • OS - Windows 10 -- 21H2 :  19044.2846  --  Windows Feature Experience Pack 120.2212.4190.0
    • GPU  -3080TI    
  • Description of the bug-------------------.  
    • Expected Behavior
      • Brand New 1st flight - STOCK02_Kerbal2  :  Bill Kerman :  
      • velocity - 2194 m/s  at  307,540  m
      • Ship no active thrust +  no time changes  or speedup + Bill Kerman EVA selected  + Very first flight w/stock vessel.  
        • 1.  select EVA on bill Kerman -  physics goes BALLISTIC.  ship destroy errors + no fuel errors. and its hilarious but really disappointing since its literally 10 min into brand new campaign w/stock vessel.   
        • Result:
        • Messages critical:   Stock02_kerbal2 is near maneuver node? (isnt one)  not sure how but sure. 
        • Vessel Stock02_Kerbal2, lost control due to not enough crew.    flight time 00:10:09    on  4/12/23 at 6:12pm MST
        • P.a.i.g.e.  - vessel no longer crewed ( ship blew into pieces and at very high speed) -  cannot change course....didnt try to. 
    • Observed Behavior
      • pure chaos due to physics love up. moment bill touches polygons of ship external. (cant even see him anymore...invisible oir probably by duna once im done typing....??) 
  • Steps to Replicate
    • 1.  New career    name, colors, etc all defaults but  new carrier hints turned off. 
    • directly to launchpad > Select "STOCK02_Kerbal2 " ship
    • launch,  Stage 1 disconnect (boosters) ,  stage 2  disconnect @ full throttle,  go to orbit.   Create maneuver node.  complete it....then when just floating in orbit....Bill Kerman EVA button at top right of screen. =   Physics goes insanely haywire. 
  • Fixes / Workarounds (if known..)
    • thoughts and prayers + no ego or hope
  • A list of ALL mods.  If the list is long, please consider using a spoiler window.
    • none.  pure vanilla, patch just completed at 6pm MST my time.  event happened at 612pm.   No reboot between
  • Other Notes / Screenshots / Log Files (if possible..)
    • YALL LITERALLY DONT ALLOW ATTACHMENTS....I HAVE LOGS AND IMAGES......till i delete the campaign that is.    heres a copy paste of entire log:
